---
description: Use local SOCKS proxy for A8c GitHub enterprise instance gh commands
alwaysApply: true
---

# GitHub A8C Proxy

- When running `gh` commands against A8c GitHub enterprise instance, set: `HTTPS_PROXY="socks5://127.0.0.1:8080"`.
- Apply the proxy for all GitHub operations on that host (for example PR, issue, and checks commands).
- Do not force this proxy for unrelated hosts unless explicitly requested.
